        <title type="html"><![CDATA[《Django4.0源码学习》- runserver命令]]></title>
        <id>https://zzggtt.github.io/uNL5ZC6-I/</id>
        <link href="https://zzggtt.github.io/uNL5ZC6-I/">
        </link>
        <updated>2023-01-20T07:25:47.000Z</updated>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="前置知识-wsgi">前置知识-WSGI</h1>
<p>Web请求流程图：<br>
<img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/34439782/1674130136946-ffd879b3-8243-47ba-ad80-519a8931918f.png#averageHue=%23dbdbdb&amp;clientId=uea650011-75d3-4&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=1&amp;crop=1&amp;from=paste&amp;height=396&amp;id=u78539615&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=image.png&amp;originHeight=792&amp;originWidth=2240&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=1&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=true&amp;size=104059&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=uc16f7d19-10ae-4152-9e9d-68c881dea5c&amp;title=%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8EDjango%E7%9A%84Web%E8%AF%B7%E6%B1%82%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%E5%9B%BE&amp;width=1120" alt="image.png" title="基于Django的Web请求流程图" loading="lazy"><br>
首先我们需要思考一个问题，为什么 <code>Flask/Django</code> 编写的Web应用程序在 <code>uWSGI </code>或者 <code>gunicorn</code> 上都可以运行呢？<br>
答案就是它们都遵循了一个标准的接口，即 <a href="https://peps.python.org/pep-3333/#abstract">WSGI-PEPE3333</a> ，基于WSGI协议，可以促进Web服务器和Web应用程序或框架之间的可移植性：</p>
<blockquote>
<p>This document specifies a proposed standard interface between web servers and Python web applications or frameworks, to promote web application portability across a variety of web servers.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>下面是基于WSGI实现的简单的例子：</p>
<pre><code class="language-python">from wsgiref.simple_server import make_server

HELLO_WORLD = b&quot;Hello world!\n&quot;

&quot;&quot;&quot;
application：应用程序或者框架，是一个可调用的对象
接受两个参数：
   -- environ: 包含WSGI环境信息的字典
   -- start_response: 生成响应的WSGI回调函数,接受两个参数status和response_headers
&quot;&quot;&quot;
def application(environ, start_response):
    status = '200 OK'
    response_headers = [('Content-type', 'text/plain')]
    start_response(status, response_headers)
    return [HELLO_WORLD]


if __name__ == &quot;__main__&quot;:
    # 基于wsgiref.simple_server模块实现一个简单的Web Server
    # 客户端的请求转发到application进行处理
    httpd = make_server('127.0.0.1', 9999, application)
    print(&quot;Serving HTTP on 127.0.0.1 port 9999...&quot;)
    httpd.serve_forever()
</code></pre>
<h1 id="runserver命令">runserver命令</h1>
<p>前面已经了解过Django命令的执行过程，接下来我们将从runserver命令调用的核心函数开始。runserver命令最终调用的是django/core/management/commands/runserver.py 中Command类的handler()方法。</p>
<h2 id="命令执行流程">命令执行流程</h2>
<p>runserver命令中Command对象调用handler()方法运行的流程如图：<br>
<img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/34439782/1674135456572-cd1a3405-05fb-4f54-b501-88b26526b445.png#averageHue=%23e3e3e3&amp;clientId=uea650011-75d3-4&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=1&amp;crop=1&amp;from=ui&amp;id=u9186e69e&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=iShot_2023-01-19_21.37.27.png&amp;originHeight=1240&amp;originWidth=2450&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=1&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=false&amp;size=265524&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=ue3468afc-39cc-47ff-aeaf-1ec1c3e7c76&amp;title=" alt="iShot_2023-01-19_21.37.27.png" loading="lazy"></p>
<h2 id="inner_run">inner_run()</h2>
<p>在inner_run()方法中，将会出现我们熟悉的控制台打印信息：<br>
<img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/34439782/1674135660500-4c205513-e313-4e09-8689-c9c8e617ffc5.png#averageHue=%23181717&amp;clientId=uea650011-75d3-4&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=1&amp;crop=1&amp;from=ui&amp;id=u0adb557c&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=iShot_2023-01-19_21.40.48.png&amp;originHeight=1608&amp;originWidth=2050&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=1&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=false&amp;size=454696&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=u34808f0f-4c90-4f6a-9165-b1f7e994636&amp;title=" alt="iShot_2023-01-19_21.40.48.png" loading="lazy"><br>
关键的是获取handler的	get_handler()方法，以及调用django/core/server/basehttp.py中的run()方法：<br>
<img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/34439782/1674135777722-b518436b-63a0-46e1-aee9-c3a0939f5b7f.png#averageHue=%23141414&amp;clientId=uea650011-75d3-4&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=1&amp;crop=1&amp;from=ui&amp;id=u5f45fc0b&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=iShot_2023-01-19_21.42.51.png&amp;originHeight=748&amp;originWidth=1462&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=1&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=false&amp;size=139026&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=u4c41942c-b6c1-4976-a179-1ee921ea603&amp;title=" alt="iShot_2023-01-19_21.42.51.png" loading="lazy"></p>
<h2 id="handler变量">handler变量</h2>
<p>self.get_handler()方法会调用django/core/servers/basehttp.py中的get_internal_wsgi_application()方法：<br>
<img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/34439782/1674136116099-95b4c675-f27b-43f9-bdd8-934196db28df.png#averageHue=%231b1817&amp;clientId=uea650011-75d3-4&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=1&amp;crop=1&amp;from=ui&amp;id=u5462acec&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=iShot_2023-01-19_21.48.27.png&amp;originHeight=1222&amp;originWidth=1806&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=1&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=false&amp;size=338654&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=u3eb0b447-cd0e-4936-89c2-0d9adea70af&amp;title=" alt="iShot_2023-01-19_21.48.27.png" loading="lazy"><br>
将会获取Django项目的配置文件中WSGI_APPLICATION参数的值：<br>
<img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/34439782/1674136371355-adbe2387-d111-4add-b370-19d1ad214279.png#averageHue=%23141414&amp;clientId=uea650011-75d3-4&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=1&amp;crop=1&amp;from=ui&amp;id=u95975e88&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=iShot_2023-01-19_21.52.42.png&amp;originHeight=140&amp;originWidth=976&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=1&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=false&amp;size=33392&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=u2bff5c58-75f3-4584-a255-745bef6d5bb&amp;title=" alt="iShot_2023-01-19_21.52.42.png" loading="lazy"><br>
将返回上面对应路径的模块，application就是get_wsgi_application()方法的返回值：<br>
<img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/34439782/1674136479550-cd918008-0675-464d-a25b-93ab59203501.png#averageHue=%23181716&amp;clientId=uea650011-75d3-4&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=1&amp;crop=1&amp;from=ui&amp;id=u7ff598bd&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=iShot_2023-01-19_21.54.32.png&amp;originHeight=906&amp;originWidth=1776&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=1&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=false&amp;size=180606&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=uece24e3d-b6fb-4e54-89a8-3186befe4ee&amp;title=" alt="iShot_2023-01-19_21.54.32.png" loading="lazy"><br>
当app_path为None时，也就是Django没有配置该参数，返回的结果也是一样的(对应代码43、44行)。<br>
get_wsgi_application()方法源码如下，可以看出application变量是一个WSGIHandler对象：<br>
<img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/34439782/1674136647836-33153722-8811-4dd9-b360-94de9ea5ccaa.png#averageHue=%23171615&amp;clientId=uea650011-75d3-4&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=1&amp;crop=1&amp;from=ui&amp;id=u4ddd35f6&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=iShot_2023-01-19_21.57.20.png&amp;originHeight=746&amp;originWidth=1738&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=1&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=false&amp;size=162052&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=udba0d7b7-7145-4853-b7c5-97c9e935656&amp;title=" alt="iShot_2023-01-19_21.57.20.png" loading="lazy"><br>
总结：从inner_run()方法中获取的handler变量是一个WSGIHandler对象。</p>
<h2 id="run方法">run()方法</h2>
<p>在前置知识-WSGI中，我们使用了Python的一个内置模块：wsgiref。该模块是基于WSGI协议开发的服务模块，我们通过make_server()方法获得了一个服务对象，并通过serve_forever()启动服务等待请求。<br>
<img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/34439782/1674137418053-aa802a0c-6821-4421-96e6-5cab20c44e92.png#averageHue=%23121110&amp;clientId=uea650011-75d3-4&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=1&amp;crop=1&amp;from=ui&amp;id=ufb8810fe&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=iShot_2023-01-19_22.10.09.png&amp;originHeight=222&amp;originWidth=1272&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=1&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=false&amp;size=59049&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=u32c0775e-dff3-4205-a6e7-a99e50951c4&amp;title=" alt="iShot_2023-01-19_22.10.09.png" loading="lazy"><br>
其中，make_server()源码如下，主要功能有亮点：</p>
<ol>
<li>实例化WSGIServer对象，监听对应的host和port</li>
<li>通过set_app()方法设置处理请求的函数</li>
</ol>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="1"><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/34439782/1674137459937-d0077313-532c-4e19-b51d-641029a9babd.png#averageHue=%23141413&amp;clientId=uea650011-75d3-4&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=1&amp;crop=1&amp;from=ui&amp;id=ud42289f3&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=iShot_2023-01-19_22.10.54.png&amp;originHeight=408&amp;originWidth=1738&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=1&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=false&amp;size=108107&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=uf6fc9315-16b9-42f0-816c-109b4971a21&amp;title=" alt="iShot_2023-01-19_22.10.54.png" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>接下来我们再看下run()方法的源码，它与make_server()方法很类似：<br>
<img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/34439782/1674137585307-833c3e3e-da52-41fa-9465-bdf533401756.png#averageHue=%23141414&amp;clientId=uea650011-75d3-4&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=1&amp;crop=1&amp;from=ui&amp;id=u24cb0073&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=iShot_2023-01-19_22.12.58.png&amp;originHeight=744&amp;originWidth=2132&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=1&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=false&amp;size=245388&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=u49b4723d-d979-4109-8c7e-0e7a9f702c1&amp;title=" alt="iShot_2023-01-19_22.12.58.png" loading="lazy"><br>
其中httpd_cls是django/core/servers/basehttp.py下的WSGIServer类，阅读其源码可以知道其继承自wsgiref模块下的WSGIServer，它拓展了初始化方法和处理错误请求的方法：<br>
<img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/34439782/1674137854393-5d81fcff-17e5-49da-a5e2-3aa416520c7b.png#averageHue=%23161515&amp;clientId=uea650011-75d3-4&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=1&amp;crop=1&amp;from=ui&amp;id=ud6b8496b&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=iShot_2023-01-19_22.17.28.png&amp;originHeight=904&amp;originWidth=1720&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=1&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=false&amp;size=234376&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=u76ee3fd4-4ef2-40d6-8201-1877ef7eb3f&amp;title=" alt="iShot_2023-01-19_22.17.28.png" loading="lazy"><br>
wsgi_handler是前面传入的handler变量也就是WSGIHandler对象，而WSGIHandler对象实现了__call__魔术方法，对象可以像函数一样被调用，所以Django中所有请求处理的源头就是这里：<br>
<img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/34439782/1674138104472-bf7ac68c-2521-4197-b207-74d73433cf81.png#averageHue=%23171716&amp;clientId=uea650011-75d3-4&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=1&amp;crop=1&amp;from=ui&amp;id=u2de6a46d&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=iShot_2023-01-19_22.21.38.png&amp;originHeight=1510&amp;originWidth=1914&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=1&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=false&amp;size=410873&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=u491a4ea2-2aee-40f7-bff1-fc792313cb7&amp;title=" alt="iShot_2023-01-19_22.21.38.png" loading="lazy"></p>
<h2 id="总结">总结</h2>
<p>runserver命令本质上是对wsgiref模块的封装，Django对于整个请求的处理源头连再django/core/handlers/wsgi.py中WSGIHandler对象的__call__方法</p>
]]></content>
