    <entry>
        <title type="html"><![CDATA[《Django4.0源码学习》- startproject命令]]></title>
        <id>https://zzggtt.github.io/7agC-DLGm/</id>
        <link href="https://zzggtt.github.io/7agC-DLGm/">
        </link>
        <updated>2023-01-15T14:51:06.000Z</updated>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>:::info<br>
在命令执行过程的基础上，开始对 django-admin startproject 命令背后执行原理进行追踪学习。<br>
:::</p>
<p>经过前面学习后，我们知道命令执行最终会调用对应模块下Command类的 handler() 方法，stratproject的源码如下：<br>
<img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/34439782/1673497222268-94df4dd2-11bb-42b6-9cf1-53cf8346d8e9.png#averageHue=%23181717&amp;clientId=uef7e59f6-120d-4&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=1&amp;crop=1&amp;from=paste&amp;height=590&amp;id=ubd27b0e5&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=image.png&amp;originHeight=590&amp;originWidth=948&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=1&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=false&amp;size=215144&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=ud7f0980b-633e-46d0-b2e9-c5e9255d487&amp;title=&amp;width=948" alt="image.png" loading="lazy"><br>
可以看出startproject命令的handler()方法并没有做太多的处理，核心还是调用了父类 TemplateCommand的handler()方法，该方法的几个主要处理如下：<br>
（1）通过validate_name() 校验项目名是否合法：<br>
<img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/34439782/1673498756533-4658fbee-95ce-4b33-a9c3-e47ab6666afd.png#averageHue=%23141413&amp;clientId=uef7e59f6-120d-4&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=1&amp;crop=1&amp;from=paste&amp;height=270&amp;id=ub054d2ec&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=image.png&amp;originHeight=270&amp;originWidth=647&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=1&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=false&amp;size=87041&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=ue7ad8c4d-400d-4d6e-b1ce-55bf4bbdbe2&amp;title=&amp;width=647" alt="image.png" loading="lazy"><br>
（2）根据target参数来判断是否创建项目；target如果为None --&gt; 则以运行Python文件时的工作目录下创建项目：<br>
<img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/34439782/1673498809490-6d8dbd3d-5230-46b2-b878-45dfbb74733d.png#averageHue=%23171615&amp;clientId=uef7e59f6-120d-4&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=1&amp;crop=1&amp;from=paste&amp;height=451&amp;id=u79292ef7&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=image.png&amp;originHeight=451&amp;originWidth=674&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=1&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=false&amp;size=160751&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=u719a38e8-2b1a-4108-9b6f-f655157414f&amp;title=&amp;width=674" alt="image.png" loading="lazy"><br>
（3）通过Django内置template下的Context类，实例化context变量，用于后续模版渲染：<br>
<img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/34439782/1673499028719-40299cd8-ee6d-4d15-b97f-33ef406c02b2.png#averageHue=%23141313&amp;clientId=uef7e59f6-120d-4&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=1&amp;crop=1&amp;from=paste&amp;height=333&amp;id=u776a485c&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=image.png&amp;originHeight=333&amp;originWidth=483&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=1&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=false&amp;size=69338&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=u2f796378-de11-488b-ae40-b5b45b9a8a3&amp;title=&amp;width=483" alt="image.png" loading="lazy"><br>
（4）通过self.handle_template()函数，得到用于生成Django项目的模版文件所在的目录：<br>
<img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/34439782/1673499191609-62865cb5-3340-475c-b070-82491cbd0db5.png#averageHue=%23574937&amp;clientId=uef7e59f6-120d-4&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=1&amp;crop=1&amp;from=paste&amp;height=283&amp;id=u9d6c99e9&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=image.png&amp;originHeight=283&amp;originWidth=760&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=1&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=false&amp;size=82958&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=u535c019d-42c7-47cb-9877-16f94995a62&amp;title=&amp;width=760" alt="image.png" loading="lazy"><br>
可以打印看下Django内置的模版路径，以及其内容：<br>
<img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/34439782/1673499332374-a1743ac4-2241-41a8-b5a5-4726516ff0f6.png#averageHue=%23181818&amp;clientId=uef7e59f6-120d-4&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=1&amp;crop=1&amp;from=paste&amp;height=103&amp;id=u7210e46a&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=image.png&amp;originHeight=103&amp;originWidth=854&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=1&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=false&amp;size=35607&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=ub03d4803-f3ca-4323-a69e-1fb94178fd5&amp;title=&amp;width=854" alt="image.png" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/34439782/1673499496163-cafb6698-de60-475a-a3a8-e0dedde6d2fc.png#averageHue=%23181717&amp;clientId=uef7e59f6-120d-4&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=1&amp;crop=1&amp;from=paste&amp;height=238&amp;id=udba99291&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=image.png&amp;originHeight=238&amp;originWidth=896&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=1&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=false&amp;size=60720&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=u671dfdc2-0eea-46ab-8d36-53624d19f9b&amp;title=&amp;width=896" alt="image.png" loading="lazy"><br>
可以看到模版目录结构就是生成项目的目录结果<br>
（5）后续的处理逻辑就是遍历模版目录下的文件，进行渲染并写入最终的位置，关键代码如图：<br>
<img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/34439782/1673499685397-58b66a37-7d0e-491d-b4d6-b3510dae94ba.png#averageHue=%23151514&amp;clientId=uef7e59f6-120d-4&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=1&amp;crop=1&amp;from=paste&amp;height=261&amp;id=u0561eb26&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=image.png&amp;originHeight=261&amp;originWidth=849&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=1&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=false&amp;size=125317&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=u24a1e226-6b7c-490d-a68d-68fff5f2eae&amp;title=&amp;width=849" alt="image.png" loading="lazy"><br>
先读取模版文件的内容，再通过调用Django内置的模版引擎进行加载内容，然后通过render()方法，把第三步生成的需要渲染的参数进行替换，最终生成项目文件。<br>
我们可以通过简单的代码观察下这段逻辑，其实就是Django模版渲染的执行步骤：<br>
<img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/34439782/1673500047725-8c148eb7-28f3-4abc-86eb-e7455644d3ba.png#averageHue=%231f1f1f&amp;clientId=uef7e59f6-120d-4&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=1&amp;crop=1&amp;from=paste&amp;height=151&amp;id=u0335861f&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=image.png&amp;originHeight=151&amp;originWidth=577&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=1&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=false&amp;size=48796&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=u6bb3e827-cb8e-4579-b79a-ac3bc626623&amp;title=&amp;width=577" alt="image.png" loading="lazy"></p>
<p>至此，startproject命令的执行过程就完毕了。</p>
]]></content>
    </entry>
    <entry>
        <title type="html"><![CDATA[《Django4.0源码学习》- 命令执行过程]]></title>
        <id>https://zzggtt.github.io/39J-dBcvp/</id>
        <link href="https://zzggtt.github.io/39J-dBcvp/">
        </link>
        <updated>2023-01-14T14:48:53.000Z</updated>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>首先我们需要理清Django命令执行的整个过程，然后才方便对每个命令背后的原理进行深入研究。<br>
<img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/34439782/1673432347469-62126357-fd06-4071-9518-9a4a67c588e3.png#averageHue=%23dcd5ce&amp;clientId=u8c5f9812-8b88-4&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=1&amp;crop=1&amp;from=paste&amp;height=415&amp;id=u14d98d9d&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=image.png&amp;originHeight=553&amp;originWidth=759&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=1&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=false&amp;size=83461&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=u644eb118-a5da-4b23-b279-3a1ac8103ee&amp;title=&amp;width=569" alt="image.png" loading="lazy"><br>
Django中命令一般来自<code>django-admin</code>和<code>manage.py</code>：<br>
<img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/34439782/1673426736067-3ce1abfd-fc29-4a3b-a7df-5668590402e3.png#averageHue=%23151514&amp;clientId=u8c5f9812-8b88-4&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=1&amp;crop=1&amp;from=paste&amp;height=200&amp;id=ubd4c6e59&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=image.png&amp;originHeight=267&amp;originWidth=789&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=1&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=true&amp;size=91987&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=u1d479a2a-aa3c-485e-aab7-cb6ce97c8f2&amp;title=django-admin%E6%BA%90%E7%A0%81&amp;width=592" alt="image.png" title="django-admin源码" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/34439782/1673426781430-65292cc8-1073-4ff7-8796-2b4f356cc2ac.png#averageHue=%23191716&amp;clientId=u8c5f9812-8b88-4&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=1&amp;crop=1&amp;from=paste&amp;height=369&amp;id=u3053e30c&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=image.png&amp;originHeight=492&amp;originWidth=858&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=1&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=true&amp;size=164840&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=u1728f974-380b-478d-86da-3a4408d33f5&amp;title=manage.py%E6%BA%90%E7%A0%81&amp;width=644" alt="image.png" title="manage.py源码" loading="lazy"><br>
我们可以看到它们最终都调用了 <code>django.core.management</code> 下的 <code>execute_from_command_line</code>函数。该函数实例化了 <code>ManagementUtility</code> 类，并调用 <code>execute()</code>函数：<br>
<img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/34439782/1673431468476-92cda787-0d38-4f65-8ec6-b57d2f2cab40.png#averageHue=%23141312&amp;clientId=u8c5f9812-8b88-4&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=1&amp;crop=1&amp;from=paste&amp;height=138&amp;id=u013de26b&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=image.png&amp;originHeight=138&amp;originWidth=773&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=1&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=false&amp;size=59839&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=uc888fbc9-b75b-42c0-8ae9-89fcf47ac5e&amp;title=&amp;width=773" alt="image.png" loading="lazy"><br>
上诉过程的的完整流程如图：<br>
<img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/34439782/1673432022039-44015de3-bf8e-412a-9062-8dc2e80a9055.png#averageHue=%2380807f&amp;clientId=u8c5f9812-8b88-4&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=1&amp;crop=1&amp;from=paste&amp;height=654&amp;id=u1b37caa8&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=image.png&amp;originHeight=654&amp;originWidth=1318&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=1&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=false&amp;size=320520&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=u7d2a707c-e492-4172-b2fb-6dada063808&amp;title=&amp;width=1318" alt="image.png" loading="lazy"></p>
<h2 id="输入">输入</h2>
<p>首先在<code>ManagementUtility</code> 类的 <code>__init__</code>方法中把命令行输入的命令保存在 <code>self.argv</code> 属性中：<br>
<img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/34439782/1673432659074-3bb0c376-f388-4c01-ab89-ba55e96afcee.png#averageHue=%23151514&amp;clientId=u8c5f9812-8b88-4&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=1&amp;crop=1&amp;from=paste&amp;height=378&amp;id=u4eedeb18&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=image.png&amp;originHeight=378&amp;originWidth=1009&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=1&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=false&amp;size=133312&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=u288f04d9-d2a3-4caf-8292-101af8eb37c&amp;title=&amp;width=1009" alt="image.png" loading="lazy"><br>
在manage.py中是有传入argv参数的，在django-admin中是没有传入的，通过sys.argv[:]来获取，我们可以通过一个简单的demo来了解下<code>sys.argv[:]</code>:</p>
<pre><code class="language-python">import sys

print(sys.argv[:])
-----------------------------------------------------
➜ python django-admin.py startproject first_project
['django-admin.py', 'startproject', 'first_project']
</code></pre>
<p>然后在execute()方法中，把子命令保存在 <code>subcommand</code> 变量中：<br>
<img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/34439782/1673433025455-8fa153ae-5a4c-4993-84a6-5fc96b6cc734.png#averageHue=%23161514&amp;clientId=u8c5f9812-8b88-4&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=1&amp;crop=1&amp;from=paste&amp;height=366&amp;id=u6d824feb&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=image.png&amp;originHeight=366&amp;originWidth=819&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=1&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=false&amp;size=111435&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=u669d965e-f34f-4803-a191-930aee0cea1&amp;title=&amp;width=819" alt="image.png" loading="lazy"></p>
<h2 id="解析">解析</h2>
<p>execute()方法中间是对参数选项的一些处理，可以先跳过，来到对下面对子命令的解析处理过程：<br>
<img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/34439782/1673433160133-e3fe7b23-d0e6-4995-8647-f91cfa5e9eb3.png#averageHue=%23171614&amp;clientId=u8c5f9812-8b88-4&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=1&amp;crop=1&amp;from=paste&amp;height=267&amp;id=u86b0de1e&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=image.png&amp;originHeight=267&amp;originWidth=781&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=1&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=false&amp;size=110987&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=uba7e880c-4c06-4cb8-8135-0f52e1b65f2&amp;title=&amp;width=781" alt="image.png" loading="lazy"><br>
这里涉及了对 <code>help</code>和 <code>version</code>命令的处理过程，这里比较简单可以跳过。我们需要关注的是最后一行：<code>self.fetch_command(subcommand).run_from_argv(self.argv)</code>。</p>
<p><code>self.fetch_command(subcommand)</code>命令执行大概流程如图：<br>
<img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/34439782/1673453074370-384718ea-92cb-440d-b08b-96cdcef3998c.png#averageHue=%23a4a3a3&amp;clientId=u8c5f9812-8b88-4&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=1&amp;crop=1&amp;from=paste&amp;height=629&amp;id=u1a6e095d&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=image.png&amp;originHeight=629&amp;originWidth=1661&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=1&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=false&amp;size=324904&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=u645e4544-e7c9-4e82-9f5a-e804b65bce2&amp;title=&amp;width=1661" alt="image.png" loading="lazy"><br>
<code>fetch_command</code>方法：<br>
<img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/34439782/1673453239236-b5c22361-49b3-426f-9521-ab4f6fa52a64.png#averageHue=%23181716&amp;clientId=u8c5f9812-8b88-4&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=1&amp;crop=1&amp;from=paste&amp;height=505&amp;id=ue8338daa&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=image.png&amp;originHeight=505&amp;originWidth=748&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=1&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=false&amp;size=168103&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=u5d2a22a1-f9ac-439d-b19c-153ae23124a&amp;title=&amp;width=748" alt="image.png" loading="lazy"><br>
首先通过调用<code>get_commands()</code>方法，返回包含目录下的命令名和'django.core'的映射：<br>
<img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/34439782/1673453345175-73ddd728-b9aa-4c0b-bfa3-93e5e1002567.png#averageHue=%23161615&amp;clientId=u8c5f9812-8b88-4&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=1&amp;crop=1&amp;from=paste&amp;height=330&amp;id=ufba09eea&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=image.png&amp;originHeight=330&amp;originWidth=840&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=1&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=false&amp;size=128745&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=u5012c088-64b7-4258-9b4b-9a446e2dbca&amp;title=&amp;width=840" alt="image.png" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/34439782/1673453607940-b0261986-8a8c-4dd1-ade7-76ca34e4613f.png#averageHue=%23242424&amp;clientId=u8c5f9812-8b88-4&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=1&amp;crop=1&amp;from=paste&amp;height=168&amp;id=uf584e73d&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=image.png&amp;originHeight=168&amp;originWidth=1253&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=1&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=false&amp;size=123238&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=uc39c1707-a94c-4688-a017-d71b8420dae&amp;title=&amp;width=1253" alt="image.png" loading="lazy"><br>
又调用了<code>find_commands()</code>方法，返回command_dir下所有模块命令名组成的列表：<br>
<img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/34439782/1673453513065-c08886ef-03d5-4079-a145-7954a6815513.png#averageHue=%23191818&amp;clientId=u8c5f9812-8b88-4&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=1&amp;crop=1&amp;from=paste&amp;height=805&amp;id=u141825f6&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=image.png&amp;originHeight=805&amp;originWidth=1227&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=1&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=false&amp;size=342005&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=uae273bb4-2cb6-4bac-a113-6cd4cff5bba&amp;title=&amp;width=1227" alt="image.png" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/34439782/1673453591318-94a9f159-1642-42dd-87de-b9655c26fbaa.png#averageHue=%231e1e1e&amp;clientId=u8c5f9812-8b88-4&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=1&amp;crop=1&amp;from=paste&amp;height=121&amp;id=u593ed158&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=image.png&amp;originHeight=121&amp;originWidth=1253&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=1&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=false&amp;size=71426&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=ue18936d0-54b7-41ea-a26f-571751fa62a&amp;title=&amp;width=1253" alt="image.png" loading="lazy"></p>
<p>接下来就是load_command_class()方法，它返回对应命令模块下的Command()类：<br>
<img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/34439782/1673453790689-6e06c816-0aa0-445d-96cc-89c4b43941be.png#averageHue=%231a1919&amp;clientId=u8c5f9812-8b88-4&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=1&amp;crop=1&amp;from=paste&amp;height=805&amp;id=u27eb76b5&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=image.png&amp;originHeight=805&amp;originWidth=1129&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=1&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=false&amp;size=335437&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=uaa486fe0-4504-42f9-a9fe-553a5151fba&amp;title=&amp;width=1129" alt="image.png" loading="lazy"><br>
经过上诉流程我们知道了<code>fetch_command</code>方法最终返回了对应命令模块下的Command()类</p>
<p>再调用Command()类下的run_from_argv()方法，如果命令模块下没有对应方法，则在其继承的父类BaseCommnad中：<br>
<img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/34439782/1673453851801-f30c38a4-e1f6-430b-a4c3-8b5e0da57ce8.png#averageHue=%23191818&amp;clientId=u8c5f9812-8b88-4&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=1&amp;crop=1&amp;from=paste&amp;height=753&amp;id=fvavu&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=image.png&amp;originHeight=753&amp;originWidth=1208&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=1&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=false&amp;size=296752&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=ud9c2fab6-d504-437d-bb91-a68cebb4702&amp;title=&amp;width=1208" alt="image.png" loading="lazy"><br>
run_from_argv()方法的核心是去调用self.execute()方法：<br>
<img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/34439782/1673454094940-795eb10f-1919-4e86-9e0f-f57acec846fe.png#averageHue=%231a1917&amp;clientId=u8c5f9812-8b88-4&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=1&amp;crop=1&amp;from=paste&amp;height=571&amp;id=u4eb019e0&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=image.png&amp;originHeight=571&amp;originWidth=855&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=1&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=false&amp;size=224579&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=uabc8e978-c6d4-42fe-9cac-d7243027426&amp;title=&amp;width=855" alt="image.png" loading="lazy"><br>
execute()方法的核心是调用self.handler()方法：<br>
<img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/34439782/1673454172486-5fc3276b-0abe-4b69-8d35-113299d97c2d.png#averageHue=%2368533e&amp;clientId=u8c5f9812-8b88-4&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=1&amp;crop=1&amp;from=paste&amp;height=670&amp;id=uc172d85f&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=image.png&amp;originHeight=670&amp;originWidth=836&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=1&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=false&amp;size=245785&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=u4f11e87b-9eec-4715-90c0-f39e1f6db69&amp;title=&amp;width=836" alt="image.png" loading="lazy"></p>
<h2 id="输出">输出</h2>
<p>最终命令执行的输出就是对应命令下的handler()方法执行的结果：<br>
<img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/34439782/1673454236359-d41ccd79-c78d-40d0-a2fd-bec1b6002b58.png#averageHue=%23181716&amp;clientId=u8c5f9812-8b88-4&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=0&amp;crop=1&amp;crop=1&amp;from=paste&amp;height=851&amp;id=u1ce18e18&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=image.png&amp;originHeight=851&amp;originWidth=923&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=1&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=false&amp;size=263544&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=uecb1afb9-33c8-4d8d-a2ad-19cf945d9d0&amp;title=&amp;width=923" alt="image.png" loading="lazy"></p>
]]></content>
    </entry>
    <entry>
        <title type="html"><![CDATA[从简单的两行代码学起]]></title>
        <id>https://zzggtt.github.io/cong-jian-dan-de-liang-xing-dai-ma-xue-qi/</id>
        <link href="https://zzggtt.github.io/cong-jian-dan-de-liang-xing-dai-ma-xue-qi/">
        </link>
        <updated>2023-01-10T10:08:19.000Z</updated>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>首先我们从下面一段简单的代码出发，里面涉及到了多个知识点：</p>
<pre><code class="language-python">data1 = 3.14
data2 = data1
</code></pre>
<p><a name="cLoEB"></a></p>
<h2 id="赋值语句的执行顺序是什么">赋值语句的执行顺序是什么？</h2>
<pre><code class="language-python">class Gizmo:
    def __init__(self) -&gt; None:
        print('Gizmo id: {}'.format(id(self)))  # 实例化对象时,打印对象的标识(内存地址)


x = Gizmo() # Gizmo id: 140650247909160
# 先打印：Gizmo id: 140650248064696
# 然后抛出异常:TypeError: unsupported operand type(s) for *: 'Gizmo' and 'int'
y = Gizmo() * 10

</code></pre>
<p>从上面的例子中我们可以看出，为了理解Python中赋值语句，应该始终先读右边。<strong>对象在右边先创建或获取，在此之后左边的变量才会绑定到对象上</strong>。</p>
